    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<h1>TALITHA KUMI</h1><p>Yesu alizungumza maneno haya ya Kiaramu kama ilivyorekodiwa na Marko katika injili yake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:41\">Marko 5:41</a>). Yairo, afisa wa sinagogi katika eneo la Galilaya, alimwita Yesu ili amponye binti yake mgonjwa. Msichana alikufa kabla Yesu hajafika. Alipofika, Yesu alishika mkono wa msichana na kusema, <em>&quot;Talitha cumi,&quot;</em> ikimaanisha &quot;Msichana mdogo, inuka.&quot; <em>&quot;Talitha&quot;</em> ni neno la upendo linalomaanisha &quot;mwanakondoo&quot; au &quot;kijana.&quot; <em>&quot;Cumi&quot;</em> ni amri ya kuinuka. Marko alitafsiri neno hilo kama &quot;Nakwambia, inuka!&quot;</p><p>Kwenye injili yake, Marko anajumuisha baadhi ya misemo ya Kiaramu ambayo Yesu alizungumza (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:17\">Marko 3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:41\">5:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:11,Mark7:34\">7:11, 34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:9-Mark11:10\">11:9â€“10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:36\">14:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:22,Mark15:34\">15:22, 34</a>). Mathayo anarekodi misemo miwili tu ya Kiaramu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:33,Matt27:46\">Mathayo 27:33, 46</a>). Injili ya Luka haijumuishi misemo hii.</p>",
